trans-unit.source: Implements an underlying type cache for all <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"></xref> derived types.
trans-unit.target: Implementerar en underliggande typcachen för alla <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"> </xref> härledda typer.

trans-unit.source: DependencyObjectType represents a specific underlying system ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-clr-md.md)]) <xref:System.Type> of a <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>.
trans-unit.target: DependencyObjectType representerar ett särskilt underliggande system ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-clr-md.md)]) <xref:System.Type>i <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>.</xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: DependencyObjectType is essentially a wrapper for the ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-clr-md.md)]) <xref:System.Type> so that it can extend some of its capabilities.
trans-unit.target: DependencyObjectType är i grunden en Omslutning för det ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-clr-md.md)]) <xref:System.Type>så att den kan utöka några av dess funktioner.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen har ingen offentlig konstruktor.

trans-unit.source: Instances of this class can only be obtained through properties on other objects (such as <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject.DependencyObjectType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), or through the static method <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObjectType.FromSystemType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Instanser av den här klassen kan bara hämtas via egenskaper för andra objekt (exempelvis <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject.DependencyObjectType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), eller via den statiska metoden <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObjectType.FromSystemType%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.DependencyObjectType.FromSystemType%2A> </xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject.DependencyObjectType%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
